Description: Calculates different micrometeorological parameters for weather stations. For example estimation of
             radiation balance, calculation of soil heat flux from soil temperature measurements, calculation of turbulent fluxes
             (Bowen Ratio, Penman, Priestley-Taylor) and much more.
